=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T14:52:49.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=885da6fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"39750a795e41105cc7dd8b5b0782c4063e367527","tid":1972600,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ba5cc5ae0055dacd1f0f280ebb1f35ede78dca8","tid":1972600,"uid":346394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a69cd2e498861d4a14a564d2abd7b5382a826a36","tid":1972600,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07e6fc6cb7dd662214feed9bfeeda8286845b521","tid":1972600,"uid":346394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T17:19:39.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}